name: dagProject
runYaml:
name: dagProject

fs_options:
  main_fs: {name: cyang14}

docker_env: iregistry.baidu-int.com/bmlc/framework/paddle:2.0.2-gpu-cuda10.1-cudnn7

entry_points:
  disDag:
    type: dag
    parameters:
      num: 111
    entry_points:
      disStep:
        type: step
        command: "echo dis"
        loop_argument: [1,2,3]
        env:
          PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
          PF_JOB_TYPE: single
          PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
          PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
          PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH
  randint:
    deps: disDag
    command: "echo {{min}} {{max}} {{random_int}}"
    parameters:
      min: -10
      max: 10
      num: 5
      pString: {"type": "string", "default": "dictparam"}
      pFloat: {"type": "float", "default": 1.11}
      pPath: {"type": "path", "default": "/path/to/anywhere"}
    artifacts:
      output:
      - random_int
    env:
      PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
      PF_JOB_TYPE: single
      PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
      PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
      PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH
  square:
    deps: randint
    loop_argument: "[1, 2]"
    artifacts:
      output:
        square_result: "{{square.result}}" 
      input:
        random_int: "{{randint.random_int}}"
    entry_points:

      square:
        command: "echo  $(({{num}} * {{num}}))"
        parameters:
          num: "{{PF_PARENT.PF_LOOP_ARGUMENT}}"
        artifacts:
          output:
          - result
        env:
          PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
          PF_JOB_TYPE: single
          PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
          PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
          PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH
      after-square:
        deps: square
        command: "echo  $(({{num}} * {{num}}))"
        parameters:
          num: "{{square.num}}"
        env:
          PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
          PF_JOB_TYPE: single
          PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
          PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
          PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH
        
  sum:
    deps: square
    command: "echo {{nums}}"
    artifacts:
      input:
        "nums": "{{square.square_result}}"
    env:
      PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
      PF_JOB_TYPE: single
      PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
      PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
      PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH
  split-by-threshold:
    deps: randint
    command: " echo [1,2,-30] > {{less}}"
    artifacts:
      output:
      - less
      - greater
      - all
      input:
        nums: "{{randint.random_int}}"
    env:
      PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
      PF_JOB_TYPE: single
      PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
      PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
      PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH
  
  process-positive:
    deps: split-by-threshold
    artifacts:
      input:
        greater: "{{split-by-threshold.greater}}"
    loop_argument: "[1,2,30]"
    entry_points:
      square:
        parameters:
          pf_parent_loop_argument: "{{PF_PARENT.PF_LOOP_ARGUMENT}}"
        condition: "{{pf_parent_loop_argument}} < 10"
        entry_points:
          show:
            reference: 
              component: show
            parameters:
              num: "{{PF_PARENT.pf_parent_loop_argument}}"

  process-negetive:
    deps: split-by-threshold
    reference:
      component: process-negetive
    artifacts:
      input:
        loop_args: "{{split-by-threshold.less}}"
  
components:
  process-negetive:
    parameters:
      pString: {"type": "string", "default": "dictparam"}
      pFloat: {"type": "float", "default": 1.11}
      pPath: {"type": "path", "default": "/path/to/anywhere"}
    artifacts:
      input:
        loop_args: ""
    loop_argument: "{{loop_args}}"
    entry_points:
      
      condition2:
        reference: 
          component: condition2
        parameters:
          num: "{{PF_PARENT.PF_LOOP_ARGUMENT}}"

  condition2:
    parameters:
      num: 11
    condition: "{{num}} > -10"
    entry_points:
      show:
        parameters:
          num: "{{PF_PARENT.num}}"
        reference:
          component: show
      abs:
        command: "echo {{num}}"
        deps: show
        parameters:
          num: "{{PF_PARENT.num}}"
          show_num: "{{show.num}}"
        artifacts:
          output:
          - out
        env:
          PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
          PF_JOB_TYPE: single
          PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
          PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
          PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH
  show:
    command: "echo {{num}} >> {{out}}"
    parameters:
      num: ""
    artifacts:
      output:
      - out
    env:
      PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
      PF_JOB_TYPE: single
      PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
      PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
      PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH


parallelism: 5
post_process:
  last:
    command: "echo {{num}}"
    parameters:
      num: 111
    env:
      PF_JOB_QUEUE_NAME: default-queue
      PF_JOB_TYPE: single
      PF_JOB_MODE: Pod
      PF_JOB_FLAVOUR: flavour1
      PF_JOB_PRIORITY: HIGH

disDag.name: dag-run-000001-disDag
disDag.message: all subDag or subStep run succeeded or skipped

runMsg: begin to running, update status to running
